\begin_layout Standard
广义函数论的创立者 Laurent Schwartz 发明了一套「多重指标 (multi-index) 记号」，可用于简化高阶偏导数符号。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Notation
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[自变量数组]
\end_layout

\end_inset

罗马字母 
\begin_inset Formula $t,x,y,z$
\end_inset

 表示「自变量 (independent variable)，可以是实数（通常用 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y$
\end_inset

 表示），也可以是复数（通常用 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

 表示）。多个自变量构成的有序集合称为「自变量数组 (tuple of independent variables)」，形式上借用「向量 (vector)」的记
法，例如
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{x}:=(x_{1},...,x_{n})\in\mathbb{R}^{n}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
向量
\emph default
是一个物理概念，各个分量（通常）具有相同的量纲，并且需要对坐标变换保持某种不变形；
\emph on
数组
\emph default
只是一个数学概念，它的各个分量不必具有相同的量纲，也不一定有明确的坐标变换规则。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Notation
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[多重指标]
\end_layout

\end_inset

希腊字母 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha,\beta,\gamma$
\end_inset

 表示的
\emph on
非负整数
\emph default
称为「指标 (index)」，多个指标构成的有序数组称为「多重指标 (multi-index)」，形式上也记为向量，例如「
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 重指标」
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{\alpha}:=(\alpha_{1},...,\alpha_{n})\in\mathbb{N}^{n}
\]

\end_inset

它的「绝对值」和「阶乘」分别定义为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Notation
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\abs{\vec{\alpha}}:=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\alpha_{i}\equiv\alpha_{1}+\cdots+\alpha_{n}\qquad\vec{\alpha}!:=\prod_{i=1}^{n}(\alpha_{i}!)\equiv(\alpha_{1}!)\cdots(\alpha_{n}!)
\]

\end_inset

特别地，记
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{0}:=(0,...,0)\qquad\vec{1}:=(1,...,1)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Notation
两个 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 重指标一般不能比较大小，但是可以定义一种「偏序 (partial order)」关系：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{\alpha}\le\vec{\beta}\iff\alpha_{i}\le\beta_{i},\;\forall\,i=1,...,n
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Notation
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[多项式]
\end_layout

\end_inset

以
\emph on
多重指标
\emph default
为「指数 (power)」的
\emph on
自变量数组
\emph default
，表示一个「单项式 (monomial)」：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Notation
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}:=\prod_{i=1}^{n}x_{i}^{\alpha_{i}}\equiv x_{1}^{\alpha_{1}}\cdots x_{n}^{\alpha_{n}}
\]

\end_inset

如果以 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{\vec{\alpha}}:=C_{\alpha_{1}\cdots\alpha_{n}}$
\end_inset

 表示 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}$
\end_inset

 的系数，则「
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 度多项式 (
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

-th degree polynomial)」可以表示为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
P(\vec{x})=\sum_{\abs{\vec{\alpha}}\le m}C_{\vec{\alpha}}\vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}\equiv\sum_{\sum_{i=1}^{n}\alpha_{i}\le m}C_{\alpha_{1}\cdots\alpha_{n}}x_{1}^{\alpha_{1}}\cdots x_{n}^{\alpha_{n}}
\]

\end_inset

如果指数是带
\emph on
二元关系符
\emph default
的字母或数字，则理解为集合：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{x}^{=m}:=\left\{ \vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}:\abs{\vec{\alpha}}=m\right\} \qquad\vec{x}^{<m}:=\left\{ \vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}:\abs{\vec{\alpha}}<m\right\} 
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark*
最后一个约定是为了避免混淆与「张量积 (tensor product)」混淆：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{x}^{=2}:=\left\{ \vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}:\abs{\vec{\alpha}}=2\right\} \qquad\vec{x}^{2}:=\vec{x}\vec{x}\equiv\vec{x}\otimes\vec{x}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[二项式展开]
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于实数 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y\in\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

 及整数
\begin_inset Foot
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
可以推广到实数指标，只不过二项式系数需要用 Gamma 函数重新定义。
\end_layout

\end_inset

指标 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\in\mathbb{N}$
\end_inset

，有以下「二项式展开」公式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
(x+y)^{m}=\sum_{\kappa\in K(\alpha)}\binom{\alpha}{\kappa}x^{\kappa}y^{\alpha-\kappa}\qquad\binom{\alpha}{\kappa}:=\frac{\kappa!}{\kappa!(\alpha-\kappa)!}\qquad K(\alpha):=\left\{ \kappa\in\mathbb{N}:\kappa\le\alpha\right\} \label{eq:Binomial::Scalar}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

对于数组 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x},\vec{y}\in\mathbb{R}^{n}$
\end_inset

 及多重指标 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{\alpha}\in\mathbb{N}^{n}$
\end_inset

，有形式上几乎完全相同的结论：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
(\vec{x}+\vec{y})^{\vec{\alpha}}=\sum_{\vec{\kappa}\in K(\vec{\alpha})}\vec{x}^{\vec{\kappa}}\vec{y}^{\vec{\alpha}-\vec{\kappa}}\qquad\binom{\vec{\alpha}}{\vec{\kappa}}:=\frac{\vec{\alpha}!}{\vec{\kappa}!(\vec{\alpha}-\vec{\kappa})!}\qquad K(\vec{\alpha}):=\left\{ \vec{\kappa}\in\mathbb{N}^{n}:\vec{\kappa}\le\vec{\alpha}\right\} \label{eq:Binomial::Vector}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:Binomial::Scalar"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 式可以推广到多项式展开：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[多项式展开]
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个实数 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1},...,x_{n}\in\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

 及整数指标 
\begin_inset Formula $m\in\mathbb{N}$
\end_inset

，有以下「多项式展开」公式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
(x_{1}+\cdots+x_{n})^{m}=\sum_{\sum_{i=1}^{n}\alpha_{i}=m}\frac{m!}{(\alpha_{1}!)\cdots(\alpha_{n}!)}x_{1}^{\alpha_{1}}\cdots x_{n}^{\alpha_{n}}\iff\vec{x}^{m}=\sum_{\abs{\vec{\alpha}}=m}\frac{m!}{\vec{\alpha}!}\vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}\label{eq:Multinomial}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Corollary
对于向量 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x},\vec{y}\in\mathbb{R}^{n}$
\end_inset

 及整数指标 
\begin_inset Formula $m\in\mathbb{N}$
\end_inset

，有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
(\vec{x}\cdot\vec{y})^{m}:=(x_{1}y_{1}+\cdots+x_{n}y_{n})^{m}=\sum_{\abs{\vec{\alpha}}=m}\frac{m!}{\vec{\alpha}!}\vec{x}^{\vec{\alpha}}\vec{y}^{\vec{\alpha}}\label{eq:Multinomial::OnInnerProduct}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
